c: 10
v: 12
t: "N’iyo umuntu agezweho n’amakuba, adusaba (mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose) yaba aryamiye urubavu, cyangwa yicaye, cyangwa ahagaze. Nyamara twamukiza amakuba yari arimo, akigira nk’aho atigeze adusaba kumukiza amakuba yamugezeho. Uko ni ko abarengera mu gukora ibyaha bakundishijwe ibyo bakoraga"